content: That's not true at all. We're not using slack at all. Who told you that. Maybe they mispoke.
Yea odd. I was there. But I think she mentioned discord.

She stated that yes we needed DISCORD and then we would be contacted with tech support to use Slack for texting. I was there too and reiterated this back to her via speaker for clarification. She replied with an affirmative. Oh well, FORWARD we go!
